title: Moonbeams from the Larger Lunacy
creator: Stephen Leacock
description: LibriVox recording of Moonbeams from the Larger Lunacy, by Stephen Leacock. Read by TriciaG. Humorous, ironic, and sometimes cynical observations of life in 1915 from Canadian humourist Stephen Leacock. (Summary by TriciaG) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (114mb)
subject: Librivox; audiobook; humor; anecdotes
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
